{"tid":1967441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到channel道歉】搞鳩程班長係咪以為無事？","createTime":"2020-04-11T02:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T18:06:01.000Z","uid":154004,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6644513485adfce2d67f4bcb756b02c406df14","tid":1967441,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"事源係有個fb page (阿斯嘉特) 同 tg channel (老豆教囝影相) 聲稱 ，程班長掛國民黨旗，話佢係國民黨線眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0hyfza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0hyfza.jpg&h=9aa6bd1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5V39ykQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5V39ykQ.jpg&h=aed2a5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後人哋程班長反擊 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cfv74sX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfv74sX.jpg&h=22a32cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋就話 讀者投稿 唔代表本台立場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smL74td.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmL74td.jpg&h=26a12252&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEP46Gz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEP46Gz.png&h=902db8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要程班長道歉 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnYmptn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnYmptn.jpg&h=f31dfbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，讀者投稿你就毫無責任？唔撚洗Factcheck吓就出？咁不負責任都講得出，瞓醒未？<br />\n<br />\n到呢一刻仲唔肯認衰仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zzfcv9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzfcv9e.jpg&h=cfbeab24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>程班長已經被批鬥到想離開香港 </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acP1puy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacP1puy.png&h=a0352360&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2edfBe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2edfBe.png&h=4103582c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個Tg channel 嘅admin 捨得檢討未？Subscribe channel 嘅你哋唔該睇清楚佢哋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f9ab853285bceaf8beceee7b387c1f619728c5e0","tid":1967441,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母不負責任"},{"pid":"2c83bc661c365b1d8e7b8873a993d2357ce5bd84","tid":1967441,"uid":154004,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"仲要想話去食嘢犯法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ei6ftYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEi6ftYj.png&h=475254cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12afb9d86bc1d7493ef21de0fe31775415562ed9","tid":1967441,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"支持程班長<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"008210e64bc3bba9f7433c0c73ca5b04fa8c0995","tid":1967441,"uid":67465,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"TG Admin 只要擺出「讀者報料」就係咪乜料都就咁擺上去, 唔使自己粗略screen 一次先? 「台灣共和國」咁大嫌疑都當冇到?<br />\nOk 我當你一開始冇睇到「台灣共和國」post 咗出嚟<br />\n咁人哋舖頭而家澄清番冇呢件事, 作為多人關注嘅 fake news 傳播者係咪鄭重向受害者程班長道歉先?! <br />\n而家仲spin 去人哋打錯字態度差, 睇唔過眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一直都有追蹤程班長嘅專頁, 佢哋免費派口罩,